          <p class="sc-body">Every night ends the same way. She says "No phones. Aab jaao. Gudnight bbbu." He sends three more messages after that. She pretends to be annoyed. He says "love u the most babyyyy 🩵." She says "loce u moreee." <strong>They've done this for 300+ nights and haven't gotten bored once.</strong></p>
