        <div class="narrator-block rv">
          <span class="narrator-em">🧑</span>
          <p class="narrator-text">I don't say these things well in real life. I get awkward. I make jokes when I should say serious things. But let me try — just once, for her birthday — to be honest about what she actually means to me.</p>
