              <p>Mujhe yaad hai woh din jab tune kaha tha ki tu class mein chup rehti hai, ki andar kuch ghut raha tha. Aur maine kaha tha — <span class="hi">"depression kuch nahi hota. Bolo. Koi judge kare toh vo uski problem hai."</span> Maine woh tab bola tha. Main woh aaj bhi kehta hoon. Sirf farak itna hai ki aaj main zyada samajhta hoon ki kehna aur feel karna alag hote hain.</p>
              <p>Tu kabhi kabhi chup ho jaati hai. Main notice karta hoon. Jab teri "haa" chhoti ho jaati hai, jab messages thodi der baad aate hain, jab tu seedha reply karti hai bina ek bhi emoji ke — tab main jaanta hoon kuch hai. <span class="hi">Aur tab bhi main tere liye hoon.</span></p>
              <p>Tune mujhse ek baar bola tha ki <span class="hi">"tuu bndaa achaa h vaaisee 🥹"</span> — aur maine mazak kiya. Par sach mein, bbbu — tu jo karti hai, woh "accha" hone se bahut aage hai. Tu meri life mein aake mujhe khud se zyada khud ki tarah feel karaati hai.</p>
              <p>Aaj kha lena. Pani pi lena. Aur aaj ki raat jab "gudnight bbbu" likhegi — tab jaanna ki woh sirf ek goodnight nahi hai. Woh mera yeh kehna hai ki <span class="hi">main kal bhi yahan hoon. Aur parso bhi.</span></p>
