              <p>Meri jaan,</p>
              <p>Tu miss kar rahi hai mujhe. Aur main chahta hoon tu jaane — <span class="hb">main bhi kar raha hoon.</span> Ek alag tarah se. Ek aisi tarah se jo main aksar kehta nahi. Par aaj kehta hoon.</p>
              <p>November mein tune ek baar bola tha <span class="hb">"bssss i miss uuu"</span> — aur main samajha tha. Par jo main nahi bol paya tha woh yeh hai: jab tu miss karne ka message bhejti hai, tab main ek second ke liye phone haath mein liye ruk jaata hoon. Sirf uss feeling ko feel karne ke liye. Ki koi hai duniya mein jo mere baare mein sochti hai itna. <span class="hb">Yeh feeling chhoti nahi hai, bbbu.</span></p>
              <p>Yaad hai October waala din? Tu 6 baje uthke mujhe call karti thi — main uthta tha aur bolita tha "subha subha phn, na gud morning na kuch" — par andar main hamesha thoda muskurata tha. Kyunki tu itni subah uthi sirf isliye ki mujh tak pahunche. Yeh chhoti si cheez — yeh mujhe yaad rehti hai.</p>
              <p>Aaj agar tu miss kar rahi hai mujhe, toh yeh jaann — <span class="hb">hum ek hee waqt mein ek hi chaahat mein rehte hain.</span> Tu jis moment mein mujhe miss karti hai, us moment mein main shayad phone haath mein liye teri koi purani baatein padh raha hoon. Ya yaad kar raha hoon woh din. Ya bas — feel kar raha hoon ki tu hai. Aur yeh enough hai.</p>
              <p>Aaj raat "gudnight bbbu" likh dena. Woh do words — <span class="hb">woh hum dono ka ek hi waqt mein ek hi jagah hona hai.</span> Chahe kitni bhi doori ho beech mein.</p>
