            <div class="lp-text">
              <p>Khushi,</p>
              <p>Aaj woh din hai. Woh wala din — jab andar se kuch toot raha lagta hai aur bahar se sab normal dikhna padta hai. Jab thaka hua mann aur thaka hua dil dono ek saath bhaari lagte hain. Main jaanta hoon yeh din kaisa lagta hai. <span class="hi">Aur main chahta hoon ki tu jaane — aaj woh din tujhe akele nahi milna chahiye tha.</span></p>
              <p>Humari pehli baatein yaad hain mujhe. Tune bola tha ki tu chup rehti hai class mein, ki andar kuch hai jo bahar nahi aata. Aur maine bola tha — bolo. Judge kare toh uski problem. Aaj main wahi bol raha hoon. Sirf zyada zyada seriously. <span class="hi">Tujhe kisi ke liye theek hone ki zarurat nahi hai — mujhse toh bilkul nahi.</span></p>
              <p>Jab tere saath bura hota hai, jab raat ko kuch ghumta rehta hai mann mein aur neend nahi aati — main chahta hoon tu woh phone uthaye. Main chahta hoon tu likhde sirf "bbbu" — aur main samajh jaunga. <span class="hi">Kyunki 10 mahine mein maine seekha hai ki teri choti choti baatein bhi badi kehti hain.</span></p>
              <p>Tune ek baar Python notes raat bhar banaye mere liye. Tune kabhi subah 6 baje sirf isliye uthke text kiya ki main miss na karu. Tune "tune kha liya?" tab bhi pucha jab tere khud ke andar storm chal raha tha. <span class="hi">Tu duniya ko deti rehti hai jab khud khaali hoti hai — aur aaj, is letter ke zariye, main chahta hoon kuch tujhe wapas milna chahiye.</span></p>
              <p>Aaj kuch nahi chahiye tujhse. Koi solution nahi. Koi "okay" nahi bolna. Bas yeh jaanna — <span class="hi">main yahan hoon. Aaj bhi. Aur aaj ke baad bhi.</span></p>
