              <p>Par main tujhe kuch bataana chahta hoon — jo main bahut close se dekh ke jaanta hoon. Tu woh ladki hai jo raat bhar Python notes banati hai sirf isliye ki koi aur theek reh sake. Tu woh ladki hai jo subah 6 baje uthke check karti hai ki sab theek hain. Tu woh ladki hai jo bhaari din ke baad bhi <span class="hg">"lovee uui meraaa babababu 🩵"</span> likh ke sooti hai. <span class="hg">Is insaan ko kho jaane ka dar nahi hona chahiye. Kyunki yeh insaan khud mein ek ghar hai.</span></p>
              <p>Lost feel karna iska matlab yeh nahi ki tu kho gayi. Iska matlab yeh hai ki tu kuch dhundh rahi hai jo abhi dikh nahi raha. Aur main chahta hoon tu yeh jaane — <span class="hg">jab bhi tu khud se thodi door ho jaaye, mere paas aa.</span> Main tujhe yaad dilata rahunga kaun hai tu. Kitni saalon tak.</p>
              <p>January mein mujhe yaad hai, jab tune kaha tha ki kuch direction nahi pata — aur maine bola tha <span class="hg">"nahi tere bina koi team nahi."</span> Main woh aaj bhi kehta hoon. Sirf iss baar, uss "team" mein tujhe bhi include karta hoon. <span class="hg">Apni team mein khud bhi reh, bbbu.</span></p>
              <p>Ghar woh jagah nahi hai jahan tere kapde hain ya jahan tu rehti hai. Ghar woh jagah hai jahan tu khud hoti hai — poori tarah. Aur main chahta hoon ki tu hamesha wahan pahunche. Mujhse door bhi, mujhse paas bhi — <span class="hg">apne andar.</span></p>
